  <!-- ABOUT THIS SERVICE -->
  <section class="content-section bg-light">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">When You're Locked Out, William Answers</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="area-content-grid">
        <div class="area-content-image">
          <img src="/images/locksmith-near-me-bullard-locks.webp" alt="William Bullard responding to an emergency lockout in North London" width="900" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJU7O3P5IbdkgRVm-wppoH9-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="area-star-card">
            <div class="area-star-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
            <div class="area-star-text">
              <span class="area-star-rating">5.0 on Google</span>
              <span class="area-star-source">Read our reviews</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="area-content-text">
          <p class="area-paragraph">Getting locked out is stressful enough without the added worry of who's actually going to turn up. With Bullard Locks, there's no mystery. William answers your call personally, gives you a realistic arrival time, and gets to you fast - typically within 20 to 40 minutes across North London. No call centres, no being passed around.</p>
          <p class="area-paragraph">William's approach to emergency work is non-destructive first. Whether it's a residential lockout, a broken lock after a break-in, or an urgent lock change, he uses specialist tools and techniques to gain entry without damaging your door or frame. If a lock needs replacing, he carries a full range of high-security British Standard cylinders and mortice locks on board.</p>
          <p class="area-paragraph">Available 24/7 and based in Crouch End N8, William provides genuine emergency cover across Haringey, Camden, Islington, Barnet, Hackney, and Enfield. He's Metropolitan Police approved, fully insured, and DBS checked - the credentials that matter when you're letting someone into your home at 2am. Fixed pricing agreed before work starts, no call-out fee.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="area-content-ctas">
        <a href="tel:07809887883" class="btn-primary-lg">
          <i class="fas fa-phone"></i> 07809 887 883
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/447809887883" class="btn-whatsapp-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES DETAIL -->
  <section class="content-section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Emergency Locksmith Services in North London</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Professional 24/7 emergency locksmith covering Camden, Islington, Haringey, Barnet, Enfield and Hackney.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-4-grid">
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="sdc-icon"><i class="fas fa-door-open"></i></div>
          <h3 class="sdc-title">Locked Out</h3>
          <p class="sdc-desc">Non-destructive entry to your home or business. William uses specialist tools to open the lock without damaging your door or frame in the vast majority of cases.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="sdc-icon"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i></div>
          <h3 class="sdc-title">Burglary Repairs</h3>
          <p class="sdc-desc">Emergency boarding-up and lock replacement following a break-in. Property made secure immediately so you can feel safe again.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="sdc-icon"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></div>
          <h3 class="sdc-title">Broken Key Extraction</h3>
