        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">01</div>
          <h3>Call Now</h3>
          <p>Call <a href="tel:07809887883" style="color:var(--color-accent)">07809 887 883</a> or <a href="https://wa.me/447809887883" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--color-accent)">WhatsApp</a>. Tell William your location in North London and what's happened. He'll give you an ETA immediately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">02</div>
          <h3>Immediate Dispatch</h3>
          <p>William heads straight to you. Typical arrival 20–40 minutes. You receive a fixed quote before any work begins - no surprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-step">
          <div class="hiw-number">03</div>
          <h3>Sorted on the Spot</h3>
          <p>Work is completed on the spot in most cases. Non-destructive entry first, no call-out fee, and your property left secure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUOTE FORM -->
  <section class="content-section bg-white" id="get-quote">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="quote-cta-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Get a Quote for Emergency Locksmith</h2>
        <p class="quote-cta-text">
          Get in touch and William will get back to you promptly. For immediate emergency help, call
          <a href="tel:07809887883" style="color:var(--color-accent); font-weight:700;">07809 887 883</a> now.
